<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Work Anniversary</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .milestone-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #171717 0%, #404040 100%);
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .milestone-years {
            font-size: 52px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .milestone-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            opacity: 0.85;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .page-title {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 0 8px 0;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #737373;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .appreciation-message {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #525252;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            color: #737373;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Employee Management System</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="page-title">Happy Work Anniversary! 🎊</h1>

            <div class="milestone-banner">
                <div class="milestone-years">{{yearsOfService}}</div>
                <div class="milestone-label">{{#if (eq yearsOfService 1)}}Year{{else}}Years{{/if}} with {{companyName}}</div>
            </div>

            <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

            <p>Today marks <strong>{{yearsOfService}} {{#if (eq yearsOfService 1)}}year{{else}}years{{/if}}</strong> since you joined us. This is a milestone worth celebrating, and we want you to know how much your contribution means to the entire team.</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Employee Name:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{employeeName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Date of Joining:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{joinDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Years of Service:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{yearsOfService}} {{#if (eq yearsOfService 1)}}year{{else}}years{{/if}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="appreciation-message">
                "Your dedication, hard work, and commitment over the past {{yearsOfService}} {{#if (eq yearsOfService 1)}}year{{else}}years{{/if}} have made a real difference. Thank you for being an integral part of {{companyName}}. We look forward to many more years of shared success."
            </div>

            <p>Here's to continued growth and success together. Thank you for everything you do!</p>

            <p>Warm regards,<br><strong>The {{companyName}} HR Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Employee Management System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
